{"tid":2248580,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"驚見火辣韓團歪樓照！Jennie 自拍穿「超寬鬆睡衣」粉絲崩潰","createTime":"2020-10-18T16:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T18:45:14.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ddeb423cb41da087a8ec338f1193cfa62427a934","tid":2248580,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/18/201018-14763-1-ZKCzq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F18%2F201018-14763-1-ZKCzq.jpg&h=c1c1499c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK 中的成員 Jennie 一向以性感火辣的造型為個人特色，近日卻有一張她身穿「超居家寬鬆睡衣」的照片外流，讓許多粉絲看傻了。<br />\n<br />\n辣團 BLACKPINK 中的性感擔當 Jennie，時常利用個人 IG 分享登台辣照，像是昨天曝光的一襲黑色短洋裝造型，蕾絲邊的設計細節已經夠讓人噴鼻血了，加上裙擺短至腿根的剪裁，搭配 Jennie 性感撩人的拍照 POSE，讓一系列美照的火辣度衝到最高點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/18/201018-14763-2-qarvG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F18%2F201018-14763-2-qarvG.jpg&h=9297840a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/18/201018-14763-3-8ZD13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F18%2F201018-14763-3-8ZD13.jpg&h=5e1d279e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過同一時間 Jennie 竟然大方曝光了自己的居家休閒照，身穿超寬鬆的成套運動服，綁著隨興的丸子頭，與性感辣照相差十萬八千里，不少粉絲截圖後傻眼留言「這是剛睡醒吧」、「她不是 Jennie」、「女神下戲後大概就是這樣」、「這一定是睡衣」。<br />\n<br />\n其實後來有粉絲起底 Jennie 這套休閒服，是來自韓國小眾品牌 Nieeh，過去時常出現在 Jennie 的穿搭造型中，有部分網友甚至猜測這是 Jennie 與好友 Chahee 共同創立的品牌，雖未經證實，但因為 Jennie 的愛用讓這品牌獲得許多好評及追隨，即使是寬鬆的睡衣款式，也同樣掀起流行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/10/18/201018-14763-4-O6J7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F10%2F18%2F201018-14763-4-O6J7f.jpg&h=41d95541&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1abba9cfa8794cd641087f0526563ba770482edf","tid":2248580,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T16:52:39.000Z","msg":"色狗死全家🙏🏻"},{"pid":"0ee58e63923f0319a1fcab796c57adb46f17a0de","tid":2248580,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T17:28:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bb20fda1ac909f1cb65f61d761726af021a4aa8","tid":2248580,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T18:42:05.000Z","msg":"老闆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55be87785de1131ebf8bde1b58b8593801668a6","tid":2248580,"uid":370019,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5jPNC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5jPNC2.jpg&h=72bc24e5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}